import React from 'react'
import { StyleSheet, View } from 'react-native'

const Login = () => {
    return (
        <View style={Styles.container}>
            <View style={Styles.containerAfter}></View>
            <View style={Styles.containerBefore}></View>
        </View>
    )
}

const Styles = StyleSheet.create({
    container: {
        width: '100%',
        height: '50%',
        alignSelf: 'center',
        marginTop: 150,
        backgroundColor: 'green',
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 50,
      },
      containerBefore: {
        backgroundColor: 'red',
        position: 'absolute',
        top: 0,
        left: 0,
        width: '50%',
        height: 30,
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderColor: 'red',
        borderStyle: 'solid',
        borderBottomRightRadius: 25,
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 25,
      },
      containerAfter: {
        backgroundColor: 'white',
        position: 'absolute',
        top: '80%',
        right: 0,
        left: '55%',
        width: '50%',
        height: '30%',
        borderWidth: 1,
        borderColor: 'black',
        borderStyle: 'solid',
        borderBottomRightRadius: 100,
        borderBottomLeftRadius: 100,
        
      }
})

export default Login
